{"tid":1881100,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"少女時代回歸？老么徐玄忍不住「劇透」粉絲狂刷留言","createTime":"2020-02-15T10:16:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T11:22:22.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"13e9253073a1ac5164d293dfc52a8c702c3f762b","tid":1881100,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T10:16:18.000Z","msg":"說起韓國女團的經典，「少女時代」絕對是其中翹楚！不只是女團的模範，而且雖然成員近年各奔東西，但彼此感情還是好得不得了。而老么成員徐玄日前突然在Instagram發文：「大家期盼的那個，再等一下子，知道是什麼吧？」引起粉絲暴動狂刷留言直呼：要回歸了？<br />\n<br />\n其實網友會「多想」不是沒有原因，前幾天少時隊長太妍也在Instagram發了限時動態說：「人生就是『突如其來』。」兩人接連「意有所指」，難怪不只SONE粉絲超期待，連網友都掀起熱議。<br />\n<br />\n對於徐玄的「劇透」，也有不少死忠粉絲直接表示，徐玄和太妍說的應該是不一樣的事情，「我記得徐玄有新戲劇，應該是在說新作品」、「真的好期待啊！雖然知道不可能但就是忍不住期待」、「我也希望是完整體回歸」。<br />\n<br />\n還有不少粉絲點名「我們老么」越來越漂亮了，尤其是日前她前往峇里島度假的美照，不只換上泳裝大秀美背，酥胸美腿更是大放送！<br />\n<br />\n以前總是甩不掉嬰兒肥的徐玄，還曾被毒舌網友笑是「豬臉」，後來靠著營養師協助調整飲食，直接狠甩變成錐子臉！其中她最推薦兩種飲食：<br />\n<br />\n1、地瓜取代白米<br />\n徐玄曾透露自己超級愛吃地瓜，更曾直接在一天三餐中、其中一餐只吃地瓜果腹！含有高纖維的地瓜，營養價值高又有飽足感，最適合用來取代白飯或麵包當主食。<br />\n<br />\n2、喝蔬果汁取代甜食<br />\n也愛吃甜食的徐玄，用蔬果汁來滿足自己想吃甜的慾望！她經常喝的有蘋果、香蕉、花椰菜打成的蔬果汁或是香蕉加上豆腐打成奶昔，不只有營養、熱量也低，加上香蕉更有飽足感，就算在減肥中也不會感到飢餓，也才能長時間維持呢！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E5%9B%9E%E6%AD%B8%E8%80%81%E4%B9%88%E5%BE%90%E7%8E%84%E5%BF%8D%E4%B8%8D%E4%BD%8F%E5%8A%87%E9%80%8F%E7%B2%89%E7%B5%B2%E7%8B%82%E5%88%B7%E7%95%99%E8%A8%80-032900855.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%25AD%25B8%25E8%2580%2581%25E4%25B9%2588%25E5%25BE%2590%25E7%258E%2584%25E5%25BF%258D%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25BD%258F%25E5%258A%2587%25E9%2580%258F%25E7%25B2%2589%25E7%25B5%25B2%25E7%258B%2582%25E5%2588%25B7%25E7%2595%2599%25E8%25A8%2580-032900855.html&d=uD1rvIJwXfBqs1i1iclFxxnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=fb270368\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E5%9B%9E%E6%AD%B8%E8%80%81%E4%B9%88%E5%BE%90%E7%8E%84%E5%BF%8D%E4%B8%8D%E4%BD%8F%E5%8A%87%E9%80%8F%E7%B2%89%E7%B5%B2%E7%8B%82%E5%88%B7%E7%95%99%E8%A8%80-032900855.html</a>"},{"pid":"5f54474b236d34cc01fcc490d810db470fdca853","tid":1881100,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T10:23:09.000Z","msg":"好似有個就生仔？"},{"pid":"7315c424ff5518837d7efba2a7d512d578bc8065","tid":1881100,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T10:30:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/d31a147db3ba6ed4f10a3efaf529e2f1/c0bed1a46215e94e-d7/s400x600/f0e5fba2b3fc68efdb0f5d54f7b1a8ed82551e8c.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Fd31a147db3ba6ed4f10a3efaf529e2f1%2Fc0bed1a46215e94e-d7%2Fs400x600%2Ff0e5fba2b3fc68efdb0f5d54f7b1a8ed82551e8c.gifv&h=db07a2e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/6af761aa4caff05f1310de87453ba380/c0bed1a46215e94e-ea/s400x600/489bda3080dbe7d212cd81d54e75b7f105919053.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F6af761aa4caff05f1310de87453ba380%2Fc0bed1a46215e94e-ea%2Fs400x600%2F489bda3080dbe7d212cd81d54e75b7f105919053.gifv&h=30637983&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/845b7f17e3efa0515807fe0f3c027b66/c0bed1a46215e94e-ac/s400x600/42612405767848c98241ac1ea0f2db1480e1eccc.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F845b7f17e3efa0515807fe0f3c027b66%2Fc0bed1a46215e94e-ac%2Fs400x600%2F42612405767848c98241ac1ea0f2db1480e1eccc.gifv&h=62174952&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aca35c603ba7195aef1e40cf62a419bfeb7803c","tid":1881100,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T11:22:22.000Z","msg":"秀英拍緊劇點會齊人CB...咪最多唱首歌拍唔成MV果隻..